.SH NAME
.PP
limit \- Control the number of records returned by the query.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
\f[B]\f[I]query.limit( <num> )\f[]\f[]
.SH CATEGORY
.PP
SdbQuery
.SH DESCRIPTION
